## Start here
1️⃣ Register on [RapidAPI]({{ $env.API_BASE_URL }} and subscribe to these two APIs:
- [Fresh LinkedIn Profile Data]({{ $env.API_BASE_URL }}
- [Twitter]({{ $env.API_BASE_URL }}


2️⃣ Set API keys for these two in `linkedInAPIKey` and `twitterAPIKey`fields of this node

3️⃣ Set email addresses that should receive the list in the `emails` field of this node

